Zero point energy                ...      0.39432257 Eh     247.44 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.02444212 Eh      15.34 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
